Description: Pauper resident TTS service for Speech Dispatcher
 Pauper keeps a Piper voice loaded in a user service and accepts short
 synthesis requests over a local Unix socket. It includes a Speech Dispatcher
 generic module bridge and a small GTK/libadwaita manager for phone-sized
 Linux devices.
